    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "[REDACTED], Circleville, Pickaway County,",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Ohio, advised he is cognizant of a \"flying saucer\" report made by Mr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "[REDACTED] Circleville, Ohio. According to [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] reported that a saucer-shaped object had landed on his farm",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "some time ago, and this report eventually reached local newspapers. In",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "June, 1953, an individual discussed the matter with Mr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "[REDACTED] advised that this person did not, to his knowledge, represent",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "himself to be an FBI Agent. The [REDACTED] further declared that he has known",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "[REDACTED] all his life and that he is a prosperous, well-respected",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "local farmer, who is considered trustworthy.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED], [REDACTED] was interviewed 7-14-53",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "at which time he stated that shortly after he received some publicity regard-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "ing his report of sighting a saucer-shaped object, he was visited by one",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "[REDACTED], who gave his address as [REDACTED] Tri-Village",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Station, Columbus, Ohio. According to Mr. [REDACTED] [REDACTED] told him he was",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "a salesman of television antennas, and that for over six years he had",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "been pursuing the hobby of investigating \"flying saucer\" reports. He",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "emphasized that he had no official connection with any part of the Govern-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "ment, but stated that he had once been \"checked\" by the FBI. Mr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "declared that [REDACTED] showed him pictures of \"flying saucers\" and told him he",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "was writing a book on the subject, which would be published soon.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
